{"blogid": "124779708", "writerAge": "码龄2年", "writerBlogNum": "2", "writerCollect": "22", "writerComment": "1", "writerFan": "2", "writerGrade": "1级", "writerIntegral": "37", "writerName": "isink.", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_124779708.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "174735", "writerRankWeekly": "1106287", "writerThumb": "13", "writerVisitNum": "8009", "blog_read_count": "7864", "blog_time": "已于 2022-08-10 15:28:05 修改", "blog_title": "VScode配置C/C++环境", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p><span style=\"color:#fe2c24;\"><strong>VScode 检测到#include 错误,请更新includepath。已为此翻译单元 禁用波形曲线</strong></span></p>\n<p><em><u><strong>解决方法：</strong></u></em></p>\n<p><strong>1：安装MinGW并配置环境变量</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/\" title=\"MinGW下载地址\">MinGW下载地址</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"308\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\7910afc162bf475da8afbaee1e910886.jpeg\" width=\"272\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>选择x86_64 -win32-seh,下载得到压缩包后，在C盘解压缩，双击进入解压得到的文件夹，双击进入bin文件夹，复制此文件夹路径。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"457\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\48748edbfef346fdafb3d4ebf333b67f.jpeg\" width=\"1069\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"330\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\157ae7e4dffd4a0fa01097c5dc523ff2.png\" width=\"1095\"/></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"></p>\n<p>在Win搜索框中输入“<strong>高级系统设置</strong>” 并打开。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"351\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ac299f49a54846c6877e5070bd256396.jpeg\" width=\"403\"/></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>点击<strong>环境变量。</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"459\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\b6f71d85f8e64effa69a379e1f87f2a2.png\" width=\"408\"/></p>\n<p></p>\n<p> 找到<strong>系统变量</strong>中的<strong>Path</strong>变量并双击。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"466\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\da3a762588d147148cb0ccefbbde8635.png\" width=\"963\"/></p>\n<p> 点击<strong>新建</strong>，在空白处<strong>粘贴</strong>刚刚复制的MinGW的文件夹路径，点击确定。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"373\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\9821e4e32310470ba718795c8f391413.jpeg\" width=\"388\"/> </p>\n<p> <strong>2：安装VScode扩展</strong></p>\n<p>扩展商店中搜索<strong>C/C++</strong>和<strong>Code Runner,点击安装。</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\8c5c8ff8460c4b549090a3dac7e5f423.jpeg\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"563\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\b9d8d4821eaf4fde9572b0f9cbab88d2.jpeg\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p><strong> 3：设置Code Runner</strong></p>\n<p>在扩展中找到Code Runner,点击扩展设置。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"531\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\b91b1985ef42407f946bdb69c4178cbd.jpeg\" width=\"372\"/></p>\n<p> 在Code Runner的扩展设置中勾选</p>\n<p><strong>Code-runner:Ignore Selection</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Code-runner:Run In Terminal</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Code-runner:Save File Before Run</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"880\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\367d7c25b6964975839bde847d27a42f.jpeg\" width=\"1200\"/> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><em><u><strong>配置完成 </strong></u></em></p>\n<p>新建文件夹（命名为英文）并在VScode中打开，新建文件（命名为英文），在文件后添加后缀</p>\n<p>“.c/.cpp\"对应C/C++,编写简单的代码后进行测试</p>\n<p><strong>在运行前要点击运行键右侧的下箭头，选择Run Code</strong></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"165\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\36fa567a16554e58be35239f00bd3ab4.jpeg\" width=\"243\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"572\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\988850903af94e419985233f5b5a4a66.jpeg\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><u><em><strong>运行成功</strong></em></u></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"1080\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\847a3a38d6ab4b53810483e1d66f52d5.jpeg\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n</div>", "first_tag": "C++", "cpp": 1, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-08-10 15:28:05", "summary": "检测到错误请更新。已为此翻译单元禁用波形曲线解决方法：：安装并配置环境变量下载地址下载地址选择下载得到压缩包后，在盘解压缩，双击进入解压得到的文件夹，双击进入文件夹，复制此文件夹路径。在搜索框中输入高"}